    invalid = 0

    for i in range(N):
        for j in range(N):
            rows[i].add(lst[i][j])
            cols[j].add(lst[i][j])

            if (lst[i][j] > N or lst[i][j] <= 0):
                invalid += 1

    numrows = 0

    numcols = 0

    for i in range(N):
        if (len(rows[i]) != N):
            numrows += 1

        if (len(cols[i]) != N):
            numcols += 1

    if (numcols == 0 and numrows == 0 and invalid == 0):
        return True
    else:
        return False
